functions.label: mockServicesFactory
description: A factory function for creating a Jest-based implementation of `SharedUxServices`.

functions.label: SharedUxServicesProvider
description:
The `React.Context` Provider component for the `SharedUxServices` context.  Any
plugin or environment that consumes SharedUX components needs to wrap their React
tree with this provider.

Within a plugin, you can use use the Shared UX plugin and retrieve a fully-configured
context from the `start` contract.

functions.label: stubServicesFactory
description: A factory function for creating simple stubbed implementations of all `SharedUxServices`.

functions.label: useData
description: React hook for accessing the pre-wired `SharedUxDataService`.

functions.label: useDocLinks
description: React hook for accessing the pre-wired `SharedUxDocLinksService`.

functions.label: useEditors
description: React hook for accessing the pre-wired `SharedUxEditorsService`.

functions.label: usePermissions
description: React hook for accessing the pre-wired `SharedUxPermissionsService`.

functions.label: usePlatformService
description: React hook for accessing the pre-wired `SharedUxPlatformService`.

functions.label: useSharedUxServices
description: React hook for accessing pre-wired `SharedUxServices`.

interfaces.label: SharedUxDataService
description: A service providing data information. Typically used for handling of empty state..

children.label: hasESData
description: True if the cluster contains data, false otherwise.

children.label: hasUserDataView
description: True if Kibana instance contains user-created data view, false otherwise.

children.label: hasDataView
description: True if Kibana instance contains any data view, including system-created ones.

interfaces.label: SharedUxDocLinksService
description: A service providing links to documentation about various features in Kibana.

children.label: dataViewsDocLink
description: A link to information about Data Views in Kibana

interfaces.label: SharedUxEditorsService
description:
A service providing methods to invoke and interact with various editors provided
in Kibana.

children.label: openDataViewEditor
description: A method to open the Data View Editor flow.

interfaces.label: SharedUxPlatformService
description:
A service providing methods to interact with the platform in which this code is
running, (almost always Kibana).

Rather than provide the entire `CoreStart` contract to components, we provide simplified
abstractions around a use case specific to Shared UX.  This way, we know exactly how the
`CoreStart` and other plugins are used.  This makes mocking and refactoring easier when
 upstream dependencies change.

children.label: setIsFullscreen
description: Sets the fullscreen state of the chrome.

children.label: isFullscreen
description: True if the chrome should be fullscreen, false otherwise.

interfaces.label: SharedUxServices
description:
A collection of services utilized by SharedUX.  This serves as a thin
abstraction layer between services provided by Kibana and other plugins
while allowing this plugin to be developed independently of those contracts.

It also allows us to "swap out" differenct implementations of these services
for different environments, (e.g. Jest, Storybook, etc.)

interfaces.label: SharedUxUserPermissionsService
description: A service providing permissions information, typically for the current user.

children.label: canCreateNewDataView
description: True if the user has permission to create a new Data View, false otherwise.

misc.label: ServiceFactory
description:
A factory function for creating one or more services.

The `S` generic determines the shape of the API being produced.
The `Parameters` generic determines what parameters are expected to
create the service.

misc.label: SharedUxServicesContext
description:
A type representing a component that provides the `SharedUxServices` through a
React Context.

objects.label: mockServiceFactories
description: A collection of mock Service Factories.

objects.label: stubServiceFactories
description: A collection of stubbed service factories.
